  "title": "PURCHASING CLERK",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Manage all purchase requisition, purchase order, delivery orders and invoices.</li><li>Manage and update of material receiving in the system.</li><li>Coordinate with suppliers to ensure on-time delivery.</li><li>Monitor prompt delivery of material to meet prompt deadline.</li><li>Update and monitor import shipment schedule arrival.</li><li>Liaise with vendors on sample, update and monitor sample schedule arrival.</li><li>Maintaining and good documentation records.</li><li>Updated purchasing records, data and pricing system.</li><li>Provide support on all purchasing matters and any other duties assigned.</li><li>To develop new overseas supply chain.</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma / Degree / Professional Certificate in Business Administration / Management or any related course</li><li>At least 2 year(s) of working experience in the related field</li><li>Experience in shipping or logistics</li><li>Proficient in MS Office applications</li><li>Resourceful and able to work independently</li><li>Can start work immediately</li></ul>",
